comment: I think Jade would be considered more decorated than Simone (in these individual games, not overall of course) because the IOC prioritizes gold medals over anything else. The US leads all countries in the overall medal count, but because China has more Gold, they're considered the current leader in these games.
author: Blake Evans

comment: I couldn't be more proud of Gelya. What a journey she has had from the most inconsistent gymnast to the joint most decorated gymnast at the Olympics. She persevered throughout the quad and her hard work finally paid off. I'm honestly so surprised how she didn't burn out despite being overworked. They literally made her attend every single competition even when she was injured.
